&lt;h3&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;If you are applying with an open resume submission, please be sure to also submit a cover letter telling us more about what you are looking for in the next chapter of your career and how you hope to add value to the Akoya team.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
